body:
Can you try a few things to help us get more information:

 - Is your model slow when run in Android on regular TensorFlow (not TF Lite)?

 - If it is, can you run the steps described [here](https://www.tensorflow.org/mobile/optimizing) in "Profiling your model" and add the log output?
